.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, black, light-blue, lavender
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, cooking, board-games, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who likes lavender is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes black is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes black##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Color   | black     | light-blue           | brown | lavender  |
| Hobby         | skydiving | puzzles | cooking   | board-games |

