.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, zombie, romance, adventure
4 different games are played: canasta, domino, mah-jongg, chess
1. the person watching zombie movies is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing chess##1
5. the person watching superhero movies is between the person playing canasta and the person watching romance movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | zombie | superhero | romance      |
| Game     | mah-jongg | canasta    | domino  | chess |

