2. the person who growsazalea is between the palace house and the person who growssunflower##2
3. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| House       | craftsman | colonial | palace     | wooden   |
| Flower   | sunflower   | azalea     | balloon-flower | orchid |

