.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, board-games, gardening
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, iced-tea
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | board-games | woodworking | gardening |
| Beverage   | 7up         | iced-tea       | hot-chocolate    | soy-milk         |

