.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer, police-officer, coach
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, italian, british
1. the russian is on the right of the coach##1
2. the italian is on the right of the police-officer##1
3. the firefighter is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the italian is on the right of the russian##1
5. the russian is between the photographer and the british##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Job    | coach   | police-officer      | photographer   | firefighter  |
| Nationality   | british | russian | italian | indian |

