.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, goat, ferret, fish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, fonseca, ritmeester, montecristo
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the snake##2
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Pet          | snake     | goat | fish   | ferret        |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | ritmeester   | fonseca | montecristo |

