.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, aristoff, alhambra, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, february, march
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the aristoff-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | aristoff | alhambra | montecristo | bolivar |
| Birthday   | february          | june     | march  | december     |

