.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
4 different games are played: poker, scrabble, canasta, chess
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, snowmobile, motorbike, taxi
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person playing chess is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the helicopter and the person playing scrabble##2
4. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Game   | chess | scrabble | poker | canasta |
| Transport           | motorbike  | taxi  | snowmobile | helicopter      |

