.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, water, iced-tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, march, january
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking coffee is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person drinking water##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage       | iced-tea | coffee | water | fanta |
| Birthday   | july    | april  | january    | march       |

