2. the project-manager is on the left of the designer##1
3. the art-deco house is the project-manager##1
4. the scientist is between the craftsman house and the modern house##2
5. the modern house is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| House   | art-deco   | craftsman   | palace | modern |
| Job         | project-manager | designer | scientist     | police-officer    |

