.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, skiing, weightlifting
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, davidoff, vegafina
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the montecristo-smoker and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Sport   | skiing    | weightlifting     | skateboarding | ice-hockey |
| Cigar     | bolivar | vegafina | davidoff       | montecristo     |

 